<div style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size:2.5em;"><span style="color: black">基金会集团</span></span><br />
<span style="font-size:1em;"><span style="color: purple">意识持续</span></span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
