<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
</div>
<div>
<div class="image-container aligncenter"><span style="margin-top: 10px; color: #black; background-color: white; border: grey; width: 2px; padding: 0px 5px;"><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/aeliana/aeliana.png" style="border: grey solid 1px; box-shadow: 0 1px 6px rgba(0,0,0,.25);" width="30%" alt="aeliana.png" class="image" /></span></div>
